OmniSupervisorConfigUser.name: OmniSupervisorConfigUser
OmniSupervisorConfigUser.description: Represents the users to which an Omni-Channel supervisor configuration applies. User-level configurations override profile-level configurations.

OmniSupervisorConfigId.description: A unique identifier for the Omni-Channel supervisor configuration.

UserId.description: A unique identifier for the user associated with this Omni-Channel supervisor configuration. A user can be associated with only one Omni-Channel supervisor configuration. This field is unique within your org.
